Class GraphicOverlay.Graphic

  • java.lang.Object
    • obd.edu.pdx.mohak.ece558.object_detection.GraphicOverlay.Graphic
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LabelGraphic
    Enclosing class:
    GraphicOverlay

    public abstract static class GraphicOverlay.Graphic
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class for a custom graphics object to be rendered within the graphic overlay. Subclass this and implement the method to define the graphics element. Add instances to the overlay using .
